  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Invite 2–3 students to share the groups of counters that they made that have fewer than the green triangles.</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿En qué se parecen los grupos que ellos formaron? ¿En qué son diferentes?</q> (They all made groups with different numbers of counters. They all have fewer than the green triangles.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


